ts as old as ~10 Gyr. Even satellites with\n4-5x10^7 Lsun can be recovered for certain combinations of dynamical ages and\norbits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2011 21:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
