eys, this\nnew technique has the potential to be competitive with weak lensing shear\nmeasurements of large scale structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2011 10:19:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
